snippet.title: Archaeology Now
snippet.description:
WELCOME TO OUR CHANNEL!
We are a public-facing archaeology organization located in Houston Texas.  

We produce three types of videos for you.  Here is how to tell them apart:  

Yellow band - 'Tiny Lectures" - Original, 5- to 10-minute videos featuring archaeologists from around the world discussing topics they are passionate about.  

Blue band - "Mini-series" - Video collaborations with experts that explore a theme, giving you more in-depth knowledge about a subject.   

Orange band - recordings of live zoom presentations allowing for audience interaction at the time of broadcast.  Stay connected on our website for updates on future events.  Or send us an email to be put on an email list.  
BTW - our website gives you much more background information about videos you find on our YouTube site.  

Reach us in the following ways:  
Email:  archaeologyhouston@gmail.com
Web:  archaeologynow.org
Facebook:  ArchaeologyNowHouston
Instagram: ArchaeologyNowHouston
